Code has the following layout. (Requires GNU Octave).

initBp.m -- Initialize the neural network
sigmoid.m -- Function for calculating a sigmoid
updateWts.m -- Update the weights of a network
calcGrad.m -- Calculate the gradient of the neural network
	functions
runBp.m -- run backpropagation on the training set, and output
	training error over so many iterations
plotDigits.m -- used to plot a set of digits
hiddenUnitsS.m -- Used to calculate the optimal number of neurons to minimize
	validation error. 
